name: SVGImageElement
description: The SVGImageElement interface corresponds to the <image> element.

members.name: SVGImageElement.x
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the x attribute of the given <image> element.

members.name: SVGImageElement.y
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the y attribute of the given <image> element.

members.name: SVGImageElement.width
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the width attribute of the given <image> element.

members.name: SVGImageElement.height
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the height attribute of the given <image> element.

members.name: SVGImageElement.preserveAspectRatio
members.description: An SVGAnimatedPreserveAspectRatio corresponding to the preserveAspectRatio attribute of the given <image> element.

members.name: SVGImageElement.crossOrigin
members.description: A DOMString corresponding to the crossorigin attribute of the given <image> element.
